  "prompt": "What is best institute in Hyderabad for group 2 exams?",
  "response": "Several institutes in Hyderabad are well-regarded for preparation for Group II exams, such as those conducted by the Telangana State Public Service Commission (TSPSC). Some of the well-known institutes include:\n\n1. **Vijetha Competitions** - Known for its comprehensive study materials and experienced faculty.\n2. **Mahendra Guru** - Offers a range of coaching programs and has a good track record in competitive exams.\n3. **Deccan Competitive Institute (DCI)** - Specializes in various competitive exams, including Group II.\n4. **Career Power** - Offers structured courses and has experienced educators.\n5. **Siva's Institute** - Known for focused coaching on TSPSC exams.\n\nBefore enrolling, consider visiting the institutes, talking to past students, and reviewing their mock test performance and study materials. Choose an institute that suits your learning style and needs.",
